data.description: Unbelievable find here!  This 4 bedroom and 2 bathroom story and a half home with detached guest quarters has so much to offer.  As you walk in the front door of this move-in ready home one will be welcomed with  beautiful hardwood floors and oak trim in the multi purpose living room.  Off the living are 2 ample bedrooms with a convenient jack and jill bath.  The open kitchen features lots of counter and cabinet space and includes a free standing pantry and room for a larger sized dining table. Off the kitchen is a handy built in storage closet and the entrance to the generous primary on-suite.  The on-suite bath has a custom walk-in shower and a double vanity.  Upstairs is a large 4th bedroom and a separate "bonus room" that could be used as a home office, family room, or 5th sleeping area. There is also main floor laundry in a small mud room just off the back door.    Other amenities inside include central heat and air and lots of unfinished storage in the basement.  Outside amenities include: covered front porch, 1/2 acre lot that is mostly fenced, extra parking for the boat or camper, 21x12 rear deck, and 2 great shade trees.  The heated detached 2 car garage has hot water available and room behind it for a shop area, storage, or kennel.  Above the garage is the guest house. It has an open floor plan that covers about 410 square feet including the bath.  Please check out all the pictures and schedule your tour.
